A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 City of Frederick, Montgomery County, and Prince George’s County – Noise
3 Abatement Monitoring Systems – Authorization and Extension
4 FOR the purpose of authorizing the use of noise abatement monitoring systems in the City
5 of Frederick to enforce certain motor vehicle noise requirements; extending the
6 termination date for the use of noise abatement monitoring systems in Montgomery
7 County and Prince George’s County; and generally relating to the use of noise
8 abatement monitoring systems.
