21 (ii) Records audio when activated;
22 (iii) Records decibel levels when activated; and
23 (iv) Allows a noise abatement monitoring system operator to
24 manually review recorded audio to ensure a violation has occurred.
25 [(6)] (7) (i) “Owner” means the registered owner of a motor vehicle or
